content:
To route work to agents with specific skills, enable skill-based routing.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
Customize Application

Available in: Lightning Experience
Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

From Setup, enter Omni-Channel in the Quick Find box, then select Omni-Channel Settings.
Select Enable Skills-Based and Direct-to-Agent Routing.
Click Save.
title: Enabling Skills-Based Routing in Service Cloud
